      "imageUrl": "/wol/d/r101/lp-cv/202026166/thumbnail",
      "caption": "mwb26 Mayo p. 10-11",
      "content": "<header>\r\n<h1 class=\"du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-color--textSubdued\" id=\"p1\" data-pid=\"1\"><span id=\"page10\" class=\"pageNum\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-no=\"10\" data-before-text=\"10\"></span>HUNYO 8-14</h1>\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-margin-top--2 du-margin-top-desktopOnly--4\" id=\"p2\" data-pid=\"2\"><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/0/0\" data-bid=\"1-1\" class=\"b\"><strong>JEREMIAS 4-6</strong></a></h2>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"bodyTxt\">\r\n<h3 class=\"dc-icon--music dc-icon-size--basePlus1 dc-icon-margin-horizontal--8 du-fontSize--base du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--2 du-padding-top--4 du-padding-top-desktopOnly--5\" id=\"p3\" data-pid=\"3\"><a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/0/0\"><strong>Awit 56</strong></a> <strong>ug Pag-ampo | Introduksiyon</strong> <span class=\"du-fontWeight--normal\">(1 min.)</span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt7\" class=\"du-fontSize--basePlus2 dc-icon--gem dc-icon-layout--top dc-icon-bgColor--teal-600 dc-icon-color--white dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8 dc-icon-padding--5 dc-icon-size--baseMinus1 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--2\">\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p4\" data-pid=\"4\"><strong>BAHANDI GIKAN SA PULONG SA DIYOS</strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt9\" class=\"dc-bleedToArticleEdge dc-paddingToContentEdge du-bgColor--bgSecondary du-margin-top--8 du-padding-top--8 du-padding-bottom--4\">\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p5\" data-pid=\"5\"><strong>1. Ang Atong Makat-onan sa Espirituwal nga Sakit sa Juda</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt11\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<div id=\"tt12\" class=\"du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p6\" data-pid=\"6\">(10 min.)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"p7\" data-pid=\"7\">Ang katawhan sa Juda gahig ulo ug rebelyoso (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/1/0\" data-bid=\"2-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 4:4,</a><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/1/1\" data-bid=\"2-2\" class=\"b\"> 14</a>; <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/1/0\"><em>w13</em> 3/15 9-10 ¶8-9</a>)</p>\r\n<p id=\"p8\" data-pid=\"8\">Wala sila maminaw dihang giingnan sila ni Jehova nga naa silay sakit sa espirituwal (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/2/0\" data-bid=\"3-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 5:31</a>; <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/2/0\"><em>jr</em> 114 ¶2</a>)</p>\r\n<p id=\"p9\" data-pid=\"9\">Nakaagom silag katalagman kay ilang gibalewala ang mga pasidaan ni Jehova (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/3/0\" data-bid=\"4-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 6:17-19</a>)</p>\r\n<hr class=\"du-width--oneSixth du-borderWidth--1 du-borderColor--borderDefault\"/>\r\n<p id=\"p10\" data-pid=\"10\"><span class=\"du-color--teal-700\"><strong>PANGUTAN-A ANG KAUGALINGON,</strong></span> ‘Unsay akong himoon aron dili ko masakit sa espirituwal?’</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"f1\" class=\"du-margin-top--8\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/209\" data-img-small-src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/210\" alt=\"Collage: 1. Sister nga namalandong sa iyang gibasa samtang nagpersonal study gamit ang Bibliya, tablet, ug mga librong “Pagtugkad.” 2. Doktor nga nagtudlo sa usa ka dayagram sa lawas sa tawo diha sa iyang tablet.\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" />\r\n<figcaption class=\"figcaption\">\r\n<p id=\"p48\" data-pid=\"48\">Kon naa kay seryosong sakit, di ba gusto nimo nga sultihan ka sa doktor kon unsa gyoy imong sakit aron matambalan ka dayon? Ingon ana pod sa espirituwal nga paagi.</p>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p11\" data-pid=\"11\"><strong>2. Espirituwal nga mga Bahandi</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt15\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<div id=\"tt16\" class=\"du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p12\" data-pid=\"12\">(10 min.)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class=\"du-listStyleType--none du-padding-inlineStart--0\"><li><p id=\"p13\" data-pid=\"13\"><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/4/0\" data-bid=\"5-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 4:10</a>—Sa unsang diwa nga gilimbongan ni Jehova ang iyang katawhan? (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/3/0\"><em>w07</em> 3/15 9 ¶4</a>)</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p14\" data-pid=\"14\">\r\n<label for=\"tt21\" id=\"tt19\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt21\" name=\"textarea-1\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"du-margin-top--8\"><p id=\"p15\" data-pid=\"15\">Unsang espirituwal nga mga bahandi ang imong nakat-onan sa pagbasa sa Bibliya niining semanaha?</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p16\" data-pid=\"16\">\r\n<label for=\"tt26\" id=\"tt24\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt26\" name=\"textarea-2\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p17\" data-pid=\"17\"><strong>3. Pagbasa sa Bibliya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt29\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p18\" data-pid=\"18\">(4 min.) <a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/5/0\" data-bid=\"6-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 5:1-11</a> (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/4/0\"><em>th</em> tun-anan 5</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt30\" class=\"dc-icon--wheat dc-icon-layout--top dc-icon-bgColor--gold-600 dc-icon-color--white dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8 dc-icon-padding--5 dc-icon-size--baseMinus1 du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-borderStyle-bottom--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--12 du-margin-bottom--2 du-padding-bottom--2\">\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p19\" data-pid=\"19\"><strong>MAGMAEPEKTIBO SA MINISTERYO</strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p20\" data-pid=\"20\"><strong>4. Dihang Magsugod ug Panag-estorya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt33\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p21\" data-pid=\"21\">(2 min.) PUBLIKONG PAGSANGYAW. (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/5/0\"><em>lmd</em> leksiyon 2 punto 3</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p22\" data-pid=\"22\"><strong>5. Dihang Magsugod ug Panag-estorya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt35\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p23\" data-pid=\"23\">(2 min.) PAGPAMALAYBALAY. (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/6/0\"><em>lmd</em> leksiyon 1 punto 3</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p24\" data-pid=\"24\"><strong>6. Dihang Makig-estorya Pag-usab</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt37\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p25\" data-pid=\"25\">(4 min.) IMPORMAL NGA PAGSANGYAW. Ang imong kaestorya nagduhaduha kon tinuod ba ang giingon sa Bibliya. (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/7/0\"><em>lmd</em> leksiyon 3 punto 3</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p26\" data-pid=\"26\"><strong>7. Pagpatin-aw sa Imong Tinuohan</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt39\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p27\" data-pid=\"27\">(3 min.) Pasundayag. <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/8/0\"><em>ijwfq</em> artikulo 5</a>—Tema: Nganong Gitawag Mig mga Saksi ni Jehova? (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/9/0\"><em>th</em> tun-anan 7</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt40\" class=\"dc-icon--sheep dc-icon-layout--top dc-icon-bgColor--red-600 dc-icon-color--white dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8 dc-icon-padding--5 dc-icon-size--baseMinus1 du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-borderStyle-bottom--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--12 du-margin-bottom--2 du-padding-bottom--2\">\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p28\" data-pid=\"28\"><span id=\"page11\" class=\"pageNum\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-no=\"11\" data-before-text=\"11\"></span><strong>KRISTOHANONG PAGKINABUHI</strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"dc-icon--music dc-icon-size--basePlus1 dc-icon-margin-horizontal--8 du-fontSize--base\" id=\"p29\" data-pid=\"29\"><a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/10/0\"><strong>Awit 60</strong></a></h3>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p30\" data-pid=\"30\"><strong>8. Panalipdi ang Imong Kasingkasing sa Dili Tinuod nga Impormasyon</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt45\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<div id=\"tt46\" class=\"du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p31\" data-pid=\"31\">(8 min.) Pakighisgot.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"p32\" data-pid=\"32\">Sa karaang Israel, ang bakak nga mga propeta nagpakaylap ug makadaot pero nindot paminawon nga mga impormasyon. (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/6/0\" data-bid=\"7-1\" class=\"b\">Isa 30:10;</a><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/6/1\" data-bid=\"7-2\" class=\"b\"> Jer 5:31</a>) Karon pod, kadtong nagpakaylap ug dili tinuod nga impormasyon sagad naningkamot nga mosultig nindot nga mga butang aron malit-agan ta. Unsaon nimo pagpanalipod ang imong kasingkasing?</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"f2\" class=\"south_center\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/211\" data-img-small-src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/212\" alt=\"Esena gikan sa video nga “Ayawg Pailad sa Dili Tinuod nga Impormasyon.” Batan-ong lalaki nga gipalibotan ug daghang message gikan sa lainlaing electronic media.\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" class=\"south_center\" />\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"f3\" class=\"south_center\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/213\" data-img-small-src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/214\" alt=\"Esena gikan sa video nga “Ayawg Pailad sa Dili Tinuod nga Impormasyon.” Ang mao ra gihapon nga batan-on nagsusi sa impormasyon diha sa laptop gamit ang dakong lente.\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" class=\"south_center\" />\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt47\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<p id=\"p33\" data-pid=\"33\"><a href=\"https://www.jw.org/finder?wtlocale=CV&amp;lank=docid-502100009_1_VIDEO\" data-video=\"webpubvid://?docid=502100009&amp;track=1&amp;langwritten=CV\"><strong>I-play ang VIDEO</strong></a> <strong>nga <em>Ayawg Pailad sa Dili Tinuod nga Impormasyon.</em></strong> Dayon pangutan-a ang mamiminaw:</p>\r\n<ul><li><p id=\"p34\" data-pid=\"34\">  Nganong peligroso ang dili tinuod nga impormasyon?</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p35\" data-pid=\"35\">\r\n<label for=\"tt53\" id=\"tt51\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt53\" name=\"textarea-3\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"du-margin-top--8\"><p id=\"p36\" data-pid=\"36\">  Unsa ang deepfake technology, ug nganong kinahanglan tang mahibalo bahin ani?</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p37\" data-pid=\"37\">\r\n<label for=\"tt58\" id=\"tt56\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt58\" name=\"textarea-4\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"du-margin-top--8\"><p id=\"p38\" data-pid=\"38\">  Unsaon nato pagseguro nga kasaligan ug tinuod gyod ang impormasyon?—<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/7/0\" data-bid=\"8-1\" class=\"b\">Job 12:11</a></p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p39\" data-pid=\"39\">\r\n<label for=\"tt63\" id=\"tt61\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt63\" name=\"textarea-5\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p id=\"p40\" data-pid=\"40\"><span class=\"du-color--maroon-600\"><strong>PANGUTAN-A ANG KAUGALINGON:</strong></span> ‘Naa ba koy tendensiya nga motuo lang sa mga impormasyon nga akong ganahan? O ginaseguro ba nako kon kasaligan ang impormasyon, ganahan man ko ani o dili?’</p>\r\n<p id=\"p41\" data-pid=\"41\">Ang mga balita sa internet ug feed sa social media sagad gibase sa kon unsay atong ganahan ug sa kon unsay pirme natong ginabasa o ginatan-aw. Maong kinahanglan tingali kang mag-amping aron makakitag kasaligang impormasyon.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p42\" data-pid=\"42\"><strong>9. Lokal nga mga Panginahanglan</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt67\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p43\" data-pid=\"43\">(7 min.)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p44\" data-pid=\"44\"><strong>10. Pagtuon sa Kongregasyon sa Bibliya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt69\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p45\" data-pid=\"45\">(30 min.) <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/11/0\"><em>lfb</em> leksiyon 92-93</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--2 du-margin-top--12 du-padding-top--4 du-padding-top-desktopOnly--5\" id=\"p46\" data-pid=\"46\"><strong>Konklusyon</strong> <span class=\"du-fontWeight--normal\">(3 min.)</span> <strong>|</strong> <span class=\"dc-icon--music dc-icon-size--basePlus1 dc-icon-margin-inlineStart--2 dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8\"><a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026166/12/0\"><strong>Awit 68</strong></a></span> <strong>ug Pag-ampo</strong></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n",
